# Used Hyperbaric Chamber Atlanta — Cloudflare Pages _redirects
#
# This is a single-page static site. There is intentionally NO SPA fallback —
# unknown paths must return 404 so Google does not index phantom duplicate URLs
# (which previously triggered "Alternate page with proper canonical tag" warnings
# in Google Search Console).
#
# www → apex redirect is configured at the Cloudflare dashboard level:
#   Rules → Redirect Rules → "Redirect www to apex" (301, status preserves URL).
# Cross-host redirects cannot be defined in _redirects on Cloudflare Pages.

# Normalize trailing slashes / common variants to canonical root
/index           /   301
/index.html      /   301
/home            /   301
/Home            /   301
